- GSCO is regulated by the US Securities and Exchange Commission under US law;  
- GSCO 受美国证券交易委员会依据美国法律的监管;  
- GSI is authorised by the Prudential Regulation Authority and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority and the Prudential Regulation Authority, under UK law;  
- GSI 获得审慎监管局的授权，并受金融行为监管局和审慎监管局依据英国法律的监管;  
- GSALLC is regulated by the Hong Kong Securities and Futures Commission under Hong Kong law; and  
- GSALLC 受香港证券及期货事务监察委员会依据香港法律的监管;  
- GSSP is regulated by the Monetary Authority of Singapore under Singapore law.  
- GSSP 受新加坡金融管理局依据新加坡法律监管。
